0110490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191003%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60110490&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVh9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=f2f79570\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191003%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60110490&h=ad0f72c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191003&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60110490</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:38:07.000Z","msg":"鋪排咗要開槍，個個都第一時間揸槍上手，根本有哂部署要用.38<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上雷鳴燈布袋彈個殺傷力都足夠高應付場面，但10.1果日唔同地點、唔同部隊、唔同時間，所有警察嘅首選武器都係.38<br />\n<br />\n仲有隻便衣笑得好開心添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7376b072928d48f04c07d17bbaa3c6883b3ece3b","tid":1609950,"uid":294652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:04:32.000Z","msg":"麻包袋"}]}